&lt;p&gt;The Associate Director, Global Pricing Strategy &amp;amp; Analytics will play a critical role in shaping and executing global pricing strategies across the portfolio. This individual will lead the development of pricing frameworks, provide advanced analytics, and generate insights to support value optimization and market access decisions. The role requires strong cross-functional collaboration with Market Access, Commercial, Finance, HEOR, and Regional teams to ensure pricing strategies are aligned with business objectives and external market dynamics.&lt;/p&gt;
