&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Drive pricing governance processes, including global price approvals and exception management.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ensure compliance with global pricing policies and external regulations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Partner with regional and country teams to support local price setting and negotiations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
